The Committee shall deliberate on each of the following matters:
* Matters concerning prior deliberations on the formulation and alteration of the basic
* Matters concerning the contingency plan;
* Matters concerning domestic and overseas energy development;
* Matters concerning plans related to energy-related transportation or logistics;
* Matters concerning the adjustment of major energy policies and energy projects;
